description: Audit every CLI command + lifecycle (create/update/close/claim/release/lifecycle aliases/delete/restore/append/list family/aggregate/context/get/history/activity/stats/validate/health/gc/deps/comments/notes/learnings/files/docs/test/test-all/update-many). Map coverage; surface gaps + forward UX.
